ed="T" n="0862c29"/><persName key="A013535">釋慧警</persName>，姓<name>張</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000004787">祁</placeName>人也。少而聰悟，襁褓能言，<pb ed="T" n="0863a" xml:id="T50.2061.0863a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0863a01"/>二親鞠愛，隣黨號為奇童。屬新譯<ptr target="#n2983"/>《大雲經》<ptr target="#n2981"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0863a02"/>經中有懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/>女主之文<ptr target="#n2982"/>，<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>感斯聖莂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1980"/>，酷<lb
ed="T" n="0863a03"/>重此經。<persName key="A013535">警</persName>方三歲，有教其誦通，其含嚼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1981"/>紆<lb
ed="T" n="0863a04"/>欝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1982"/>，調致天然也。遂徹九重<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1162"/>，乃詔諷之。<ref type="person" target="#A002099">帝</ref>大<lb
ed="T" n="0863a05"/>悅，撫其頂，勅授紫袈裟一副，後因出家。氣<lb
ed="T" n="0863a06"/>貌剛介，學處堅固，充<ref type="place" target="#PL000000003781">本寺</ref>上座。拯頓頹綱，人<lb
ed="T" n="0863a07"/>皆畏憚。或於街陌見二眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g571"/>失儀，片招譏醜，<lb
ed="T" n="0863a08"/>必議懲誡，斷無寬理。後修禪法，虛室生白<ptr target="#n1904"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0863a09"/>終時已八十餘齡矣。<placeName key="PL000000057284">九子母院</placeName>有遺影，并賜<lb
ed="T" n="0863a10"/>紫衣存焉。</p>
